  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support Action for Asylum Sections of Immigration Offices and Border Police Offices (SAAS)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is providing support to the Italian Border Police in selected regions of Northern Italy through a trained pool of cultural mediators specialized in EU asylum and international protection procedures. IOM will select, train and deploy this specialized team of mediators to ensure that the authorities continue to have access to a high standard of specialized personnel so that their officers are able to function with maximum efficiency and capacity to properly assist migrants and asylum seekers in the police offices and at the air border crossing points.</narrative>
  </description>
